{"tid":1777257,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"為香港而死嘅人 我哋應該好好咁記住","createTime":"2019-12-10T05:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T07:43:36.000Z","uid":38801,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aedbbab8bc15c6930221ec780af2c266d3b1a958","tid":1777257,"uid":38801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unMEQg7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FunMEQg7.jpg&h=2768e7d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n█ 古來征戰幾人回。<br />\n1941年，#皇家蘇格蘭步兵團第2營（2nd Battalion, #RoyalScots）營總部連於金鐘 #美利兵房 #MurrayBarrack 留影，未知多少人能夠平安捱到聖誕。<br />\n<br />\n此營鎮守醉酒灣防線左翼，在12月9日首當其衝，率先接戰。12月11日，他們在金山硬拼來襲日軍，白刃戰肉搏。激戰中，日軍第230聯隊第5中隊隊長被擊斃，皇家蘇格蘭營B、C連連長雙雙陣亡。<br />\n<br />\n為數769人的皇家蘇格蘭營，最終108人戰死、49人下落不明、199人受傷，傷亡率達46%。全數35名軍官，16人戰死，11人負傷。<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n█ 傷亡最慘重的部隊：<br />\n【印】第7拉吉普團第5營（892人）<br />\n5/7th Battalion, #Rajput Regiment<br />\n<br />\n拉吉普營先是陣守醉酒灣防線東翼，繼而負責為「大陸旅」撤回港島殿後，在魔鬼山奮戰，其後在北角首當其衝抵擋日軍登陸總攻擊，蒙受重大傷亡：<br />\n<br />\n156人戰死、113 人下落不明、193人受傷，傷亡率達51%。當中，全數17名軍官戰死或負傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1030734923927942&amp;id=149029388765171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1030734923927942%26id%3D149029388765171&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cVTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=64870391\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1030734923927942&amp;id=149029388765171</a>"},{"pid":"6f93198cba9f3acc0b704a5d5af639017a8b43d7","tid":1777257,"uid":38801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"學校應該教呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fed6d176c079f5dd569fe0743080f87f3e31342","tid":1777257,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06:09:17.000Z","msg":"sorry借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男銷售員 6 月涉推跌六旬男子致死被控謀殺　控方近半年仍未能確定死因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ab7fd775d87eb74a71e6556c09680a85ac65561a","tid":1777257,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"呢班人見到自己用命守護既土地再一次被侵略 會係咩心情 唉 好想守護好香港 但香港人都仲係口頭強烈譴責"}]}